System Architecture Diagram Screenshot
=======================================

This file represents the complete system architecture showing:

- GuardDuty threat detection flow
- CloudWatch Events triggering
- Lambda function processing
- SNS notification delivery
- EC2 instance remediation

Architecture flow:
1. Attacker -> Compromised EC2 Instance
2. EC2 -> GuardDuty Finding (severity 7-9)
3. GuardDuty -> CloudWatch Event Rule
4. Event Rule -> Lambda Function
5. Lambda -> SNS Alert Email
6. Lambda -> Stop EC2 Instance
